---
<section id="process" class="process-section">
  <div class="process-inner container">
    <div class="process-header">
      <div>
        <div class="section-tag">How It Works</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Simple. Focused.<br/><span class="accent">No fluff.</span></h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        We move fast because we've kept the process lean. No lengthy discovery phases,
        no bloated proposals. You get clarity and momentum from day one.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="process-steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-title">Free Audit</div>
        <p class="step-desc">We review your current web presence, GBP, and content. You get a clear picture of what's costing you clients right now.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div class="step-title">Proposal</div>
        <p class="step-desc">A focused scope — not a 40-page document. We tell you exactly what we'll do, when, and what it costs. No surprises.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <div class="step-title">Build & Launch</div>
        <p class="step-desc">We execute fast. Website live in 2–3 weeks. GBP active. Content calendar ready. You'll see visible progress within the first 30 days.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <div class="step-title">Retainer</div>
        <p class="step-desc">Monthly retainer keeps everything growing — new content, GBP updates, technical maintenance, and ongoing optimisation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
